hamburg_radar<-
  hamburg %>% 
     select(Restaurante,Calorias,grasascal, colesterol,sodio, fibra, azucar, proteina) %>%
     group_by(Restaurante) %>%
     summarize_all(mean)

##Normalizar
normalize  <- function(x) {
  
     x =  (x - min(x) )/ (  max(x) - min(x) )
     
     return(x)
}

###Personalizar
create_beautiful_radarchart <- function(data, color = "#00AFBB", 
                                        vlabels = colnames(data), vlcex = 0.7,
                                        caxislabels = NULL, title = 'Diagrama Grasas Restaurantes'){
  radarchart(
    data, axistype = 1,
    # Customize the polygon
    pcol = color, pfcol = scales::alpha(color, 0.5), plwd = 2, plty = 1,
    # Customize the grid
    cglcol = "grey", cglty = 1, cglwd = 0.8,
    # Customize the axis
    axislabcol = "grey", 
    # Variable labels
    vlcex = vlcex, vlabels = vlabels,
    caxislabels = caxislabels, title = title
  )
}

op <- par(mar = c(1, 2, 2, 1))
create_beautiful_radarchart(mcdonaldsData, caxislabels = c(0, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 1))

par(op)
